text: H McCallum was a professional rugby league footballer in the Australian competition, the New South Wales Rugby League. McCallum's only matches were for the Eastern Suburbs club in the 1936 season. == References== * The Encyclopedia Of Rugby League; Alan Whiticker & Glen Hudson Category:Australian rugby league players Category:Sydney Roosters players Category:Possibly living people Category:Year of birth missing Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
